Code: EXEC SQL SELECT T1.NRPARCEL, T1.QTDDOC, T1.SITUACAO, T1.OCORHIST, T2.CODSUBES FROM seguros.v1parcela T1, seguros.v1parcela T2 WHERE T1.NUM_APOLICE = :NUM_APOLICE AND T1.NUM_APOLICE = T2.NUM_APOLICE AND T2.CODSUBES = :CODSUBES AND T1.NRENDOS = :NRENDOS AND T1.NRENDOS = T2.NRENDOS AND T1.NRPARCEL = :NRPARCEL END SQL
